response.overview: Cindy finds out the house she lives in is haunted by a little boy and goes on a quest to find out who killed him and why. Also, Alien "Tr-iPods" are invading the world and she has to uncover the secret in order to stop them.
response.tagline: Bury the grudge. Burn the village.  See the saw.
response.title: Scary Movie 4
